{"tid":890723,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獨食近60粒炒白果　38歲女子中毒入院　衛生署：一次過食10粒可致中毒 (18:52)","createTime":"2018-11-05T14:07:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-05T17:21:12.000Z","uid":13468,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d6a64786dfe32430712cb8e2d125a88e1c8c77be","tid":890723,"uid":13468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T14:07:39.000Z","msg":"獨食近60粒炒白果　38歲女子中毒入院　衛生署：一次過食10粒可致中毒 (18:52)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一名38歲女子，前日（3日）在太子地鐵站近旺角警署的小販檔，購買50至60粒炒白果，並全數進食，約一個半小時後感暈眩、惡心、震顫、頭痛及腹痛等。她昨到聯合醫院求醫，經治療後同日出院，情況一直穩定。今次是衛生防護中心5年來首次錄得白果中毒個案。<br />\n<br />\n衛生署解釋，白果（又稱銀杏）含有能主要影響神經系統的毒素，有報告指出，一次過進食10至50顆經煮熟的白果，已可引致急性中毒；未成熟及未經煮熟的白果毒性更強。<br />\n<br />\n中白果毒的人通常在進食1至12小時後，便會出現嘔吐、煩躁、持續或陣攣性抽搐等徵狀，進食大量白果而嚴重中毒，更可導致失去知覺，甚至死亡。同類食物中毒況多見於兒童。衛生署提醒，白果切忌生食，且只可小量進食；兒童、長者及身體欠佳者等，進食時須加倍留意。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181105/s00001/1541414957446\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181105%2Fs00001%2F1541414957446&d=%2BAsIOPlVLiug4t6yw5b%2BDqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=63629aa6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20181105%2Fs00001%2F1541414957446&h=b913c290\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20181105/s00001/1541414957446</a>"},{"pid":"7eeedf76e89a184b296f68f3de0bc9e8cd111a7b","tid":890723,"uid":123859,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T14:27:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 嘩好撚好笑丫屌你老母食白果"},{"pid":"4712170203cb13f3192dbfe890bf85007678f7b9","tid":890723,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T14:32:10.000Z","msg":"銀杏腐皮糖水<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b73b9dee637a13f8060959e1d9af0db780beeeb","tid":890723,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T14:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70d3246ccb6f50aa0fed3ca24ffa782087d646a8","tid":890723,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:21:04.000Z","msg":"賭徒有血清免疫"},{"pid":"a2bd7c334680dd0fc08e24be7d7f191cc0edb3fe","tid":890723,"uid":86383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"70d3246ccb6f50aa0fed3ca24ffa782087d646a8","tid":890723,"uid":653,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T15:21:04.000Z","msg":"賭徒有血清免疫"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-05T17:21:12.000Z","msg":"一日裡面食60次喎<br />\n仲唔輸到jump<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}